article_title: Plant seeds now to meet needs of future
article_text:
Moline, IL (61265)

Today

Thunderstorms likely this morning. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms this afternoon. High 79F. Winds S at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Thunderstorms likely this evening. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms overnight. Low 66F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author: Rick Seidler

og.description: According to the Bureau of Labor Statistics’ Employment Projections 2012-2022 released in December 2013, registered nursing (RN) is listed among the top occupations in terms of job growth through 2022.
